    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence and high decision consequence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions and submission of RH index results in the 510(k) regulatory package. No open credibility gaps identified that would preclude acceptance.",
